Once upon a time, there were two wizards who lived in a magical kingdom. With their wands, they could weave wondrous spells and wield wild weather. What would they do with their wizardry? They decided to work together and create a world of wonders! They waved their wands and willed the world to be filled with wonderful things. Who knew what wild wonders would appear? The wizards watched with wide eyes as the world around them changed. They worked with each other to make sure everything was just right, and soon enough, the world was full of wonderful things!
